Guy T. HELVERING, Commissioner, etc., v. H. A. GREEN. No. 8305. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 17, 1936. Robert H. Jackson, Asst. Atty. Gen., and Herman Oliphant, Gen. Counsel, Department of Treasury, of Washington, D. C., for petitioner. O. A. Neal, of Portland, Or., for respondent.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of petitioner, ordered petition for review dismissed, and judgment of dismissal filed and entered.
